<section xml:id="accommodations">
  <title>What accommodations are available?</title>

  <p>
    Students who might need special accommodation should receive approval
    from the <term>Center for Disability Services/SNAP</term>, and contact me
    as soon as possible to arrange suitable accommodations.
    Please note that all accommodation information is confidential.
  </p>

  <p>
    For more information, please visit
    <url href="http://disabilityservices.cofc.edu/">
      the Center for Disabilities/SNAP
    </url>.
  </p>

  <p>
    Please also explore
    <url href="https://charleston.edu/student-life/student-support/index.php">
      Students Support &amp; Services
    </url>
    for other resources available to students such as Cougar Food Pantry,
    Information Technology, Military and Veteran Student Services,
    Wellness and Well-being, Counseling Center, Student Health Services,
    and Office of Victim Services.
  </p>
</section>





